== Arabic ==
===Etymology===
Root: [[شجر]]

===Noun===
'''شَجَرٌ''' (šádžar) ''m (collective)'', '''ٌشَجَرَة''' (šádžara) ''f (singulative)'', '''شَجَرْتِينِ''' (šadžartéːn) ''(dual)'', '''شَجَرَاتٌ''' (šadžaráːt) ''([[paucal]])'', '''أشْجَارٌ''' (‘ašdžáːr) ''(pl.)''

#[[tree]]


*شَجَرٌ (šádžar) = trees in general ''(plural in meaning, but grammatically singular)''
*ٌشَجَرَة (šádžara) = a tree
*شَجَرْتِينِ (šadžartéːn) = two trees
*شَجَرَاتٌ (šadžaráːt) = 3 to 10 trees, some trees, a few trees
*أشْجَارٌ (‘ašdžáːr) = kinds of trees